        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌641點科指跌逾4%  一周累計科指跌近8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後跌勢急，恒生指數全日跌641點，科指跌逾4%，手機設備股、光伏股及晶片股跌幅大，一周累計恒指跌近4%，科指挫近8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收報25247，跌641點或2.48%，午後跌幅急速擴大，後段低見25145，瀉743點或2.87%，直迫25100關，為全日低位，今早開跌36點或0.14%，報25821，早段見25859，跌29點或0.11%，為全日高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123539_source-web_信義光能00968-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123539_source-web_信義光能00968-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123539_source-web_信義光能00968-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日跌243點或4.05%，報5760點，今早開跌4點或0.07%，報5999。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日跌247點或2.67%，報9011，今早開報9259點，無升跌，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指報25225 ，跌680點或2.63%，低水22點 ; 科指期貨報6-5752，跌269點或4.47%，低水8點 ; 國指期貨跌262點或2.83%，報9002，低水10點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交3146.24億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後跌幅擴大，港股隨之下滑，內地周一公布第三季經濟增長，投行預期增長較前兩季放緩 ; 上日美股地區銀行爆壞帳危機，市場不明朗因素增加。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全周，恒指累跌1043點或3.97% ; 科指累趺499點或7.97% ; 國指累跌347點或3.71%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪電子(00285)挫8,13%，報37,74元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 舜宇光學科技(02382)跌5.17%，報76.2元 ; 瑞聲科技(02018)跌5.16%，報38.64元 ; 丘鈦科技(01478)大瀉9.22%，報13.59元 ; 高偉電子(01415)跌5.43%，報31.38元。蘋果公司傳計劃2026年底或2027年初推出配備觸控螢幕的升級版MacBook Pro，放棄「蘋果教主」喬布斯（Steve Jobs）反對豎直觸控螢幕電腦的立場。喬布斯2012年時曾表示觸控螢幕不應是豎直的，而整個行業在十多年前就開始推出觸屏版筆記型電腦。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏股下挫，內地傳聞多晶硅收儲平台已成立，信義光能(00968)全日跌6.79%，報3.43元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位 ; 協鑫科技(03800)跌6.52%，報1.29元 ; 福萊特玻璃(06865)跌3.46%，報11.15元。今日突然有消息指，多晶硅收儲平台已經成立，平台公司工商註冊完成，名稱為「中硅產能整合有限公司」，共管帳號也已開立，將推行「以大收小」。官方媒體《證券時報》引述業內權威人士指出，傳聞消息不實。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123539_source-web_信義光能00968-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123539_source-web_信義光能00968-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股顯著回落，中芯(00981)跌6.5%，報69.1元 ; 華虹(01347)跌6.94%，報75.8元; 上海復旦(01385)挫5.12%，報39.66元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)挫4.22%，報154.4元; 小米(01810)跌3.65%，報45.96元 ; 滙控(00005)跌1.94%，報100.9元 ; 三股合共佔恒指跌幅192點，騰訊(00700)挫1.94%，報608元 ; 美團(03690)跌4.3%，報94.5元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價上報4300美元，金行股逆市升，周大福(01929)升5.02%，報16.52元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 老鋪黃金(06181)升3.11%，報828.5元 ; 六福(00590)升1.1%，報25.68元。金礦股升幅收窄或轉跌，紫金黃金國際(02259)收升0.27%，報147.8元 ; 紫金(02899)轉跌1.27%，報32.6元 ; 山東黃金(01787)升0.27%，報37.9元。</p>\n</div>",
